{
    "id":  "web-fix-i18n-prices-constants",
    "name":  "Web价格工具5页常量标签中文硬编码 — 价格比较/日历/趋势/提醒筛选器国际化缺失",
    "app":  "web",
    "priority":  1,
    "description":  "Web价格工具5个页面的ENTITY_OPTIONS、COMPARE_ROWS、PERIODS等常量使用中文标签。\n\n修改文件:\n1. apps/web/src/app/prices/compare/page.tsx — COMPARE_ROWS labels(~行72-77)和ALL_PACKAGES(~行8-14)\n2. apps/web/src/app/prices/trend/page.tsx — ENTITY_OPTIONS(~行8-11)和PERIODS(~行15-17)\n3. apps/web/src/app/prices/calendar/page.tsx — ENTITY_OPTIONS(~行7-11)、WEEKDAYS(~行36)、MONTH_NAMES(~行37)\n4. apps/web/src/app/prices/alerts/page.tsx — ENTITY_OPTIONS(~行7-12)\n5. apps/web/src/app/prices/page.tsx — 如有中文标签也一并处理\n\n使用useTranslation()的t()函数替换所有中文label，添加对应翻译key。\n\n对标: Skyscanner/Kayak的价格工具支持全球多语言\n铁律: SCP-02\n验证: pnpm --filter @zuting/web build"
}
